Leave commented to just use the default, which is[12;5Hescribed in the man page or at[13d## https://www.torproject.org/documentation.html[14d##[15d Look at https://www.torproject.org/faq-abuse.html#TypicalAbuses[K[16;4Hfor issues you might encounter if you use the default exit policy.[17;4H[K[18dIf certain IPs and ports are blocked externally, e.g. by your firewall,[19;4Hyou should update your exit policy to reflect this -- otherwise Tor[20;4Husers will be told that those destinations are down.[K[21;4H[K[3d
